Globalization is the process of international integration arising from the interchange of world views, products, ideas, and other aspects of culture. Though many scholars place the origins of globalization in modern times, others see its origins in antiquity as a process enabled by the Ancient Romans and later empires. remote working is a new trend in the world of work. It is a way of working where employees work from home or other locations, instead of working in an office. It is a way of working that is becoming more and more popular, especially in the IT sector. There are many advantages to remote working. For example, it can save time and money on commuting, and it can also improve work-life balance. However, there are also some disadvantages to remote working.
